						               													<description>Welcome to Mega-City One, a city of over four hundred million people and every one of them a potential criminal. Stretching the length of the 22nd Century North American eastern seaboard, Mega-City One is the most dangerous city on Earth &amp;ndash; a serious crime takes place every second of every day. This is a city so dangerous that it demands a special breed of law enforcer. Here, there are no police, no trials and no juries &amp;ndash; there are only the judges. It takes fifteen years to train a judge for life on the streets of Mega-City One.&amp;#239;&amp;#187;&amp;#191;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;quot;Judge Dredd&amp;quot; is a 28mm miniatures skirmish game designed to be quick, easy to learn, and capable of handling the madness that is Mega-City One, from the powerful judges to the lowliest punk or mutant.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players take turns moving figures and taking actions. Figures can be customized to use a multitude of weapons, equipment and powers - running, jumping, driving, and fighting in a crazy sci-fi themed world. You create the scenarios and take it from there.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;May your Lawgiver always fire true!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Note This game is the spiritual successor of Gangs of Mega-City One (GoMC1) but it is a different game. It is compatible with the models from Mongoose Publishing.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
